211
00:14:04,404 --> 00:14:07,092
but do not have the skills and 
techniques needed for building,

212
00:14:07,092 --> 00:14:10,500
which makes the quality 
of construction often unreliable.

213
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:14,970
Another critical problem 
with real-estate promotion

214
00:14:14,970 --> 00:14:19,580
is the price fluctuation 
of material costs.

215
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:27,390
A ton of cement can very quickly 
double the cost of concrete blocks.

216
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:33,160
If you begin with one price, and 
a few months later it has doubled,

217
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:38,259
this poses problems; it poses 
financing problems, surely.

218
00:14:38,259 --> 00:14:40,225
These price fluctuations of materials

