00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:19,864
And to provide housing for the poorest,

229
00:15:19,864 --> 00:15:23,514
one needs an intervention by 
the state, or by other funders.

230
00:15:23,514 --> 00:15:26,228
But without intervention 
from the outside,

231
00:15:26,228 --> 00:15:30,720
the only real-estate promotion 
