262
00:17:54,825 --> 00:17:56,460
There is supply, and there is demand.

263
00:17:56,460 --> 00:17:59,587
So with housing programs, 
we must find out

264
00:17:59,587 --> 00:18:02,537
where we stand, whether on 
the side of supply or demand,

