266
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:09,560
to balance at the same time 
supply and demand.

267
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:13,156
Surely, by linking together the two, 
we can achieve results

268
00:18:13,156 --> 00:18:15,790
which are no doubt better, 
